  media:['Upload reusable website images here. Edit the title and alt text in both languages, or replace an existing image.','Replacing an image keeps its CMS reference so connected content continues to work.'],
  theme:['Adjust the approved design tokens and typography. Preview changes in the sample card before publishing.','Save Draft stores a private browser preview. Publish updates the live website theme.']
